column2: Recursively assigning properties on objects may cause accidental modification of a built-in prototype object.
column4:
The property chain [["here"|"relative:///index.js:17:11:17:20"]] is recursively assigned to [["obj"|"relative:///index.js:88:5:88:7"]] without guarding against prototype pollution.
